about_us_content: We offer thorough examinations by competent doctors, as well as performing a wide range of medical manipulations and high-quality laboratory services, only and entirely in the comfort of your home. Forget about endless waiting in lines outside medical offices and laboratories. Our specialists come to you. We created the service with the idea of showing you a different doctor-patient relationship. Our individual approach to each patient aims to put their needs first. You receive courtesy, attentiveness, peace of mind, security and quality during the actual examination or manipulation, and the infinite satisfaction of the visible results remains with us.
